						               													<description>From the box:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The mystery - The Queen of High Fashion, Francesca Baldini, created a Spring collection to die for.  Unfortunately, she was found dead at her elegant FAB couture house.  Around her are the slashed remains of her  Spring collection.  Accessorizing the scene is a footprint in blood near her head.  You and 5 others are woven into the fabric of this murder.  This is a tale of high society and high fashion.  It will seduce you into the seamy side with a deadly combination of violence and vogue.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Suspects:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gloria Spoddy - She is the aloof and confident international model whose striking looks are perfect for Francesca's designs.  Is she capable of murder most fashionable?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mike Ruffone - Dangerously handsome, this ex-rock star gave up his career for the love of Francesca.  But is he strumming her heart strings for his own mysterious reasons?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Doll Chevita - Francesca's younger sister, her meek demeanor covers a violent past.  But is this &amp;quot;babydoll&amp;quot; really as innocent as she appears to be?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Minnie Kashfloe - A stylish socialite and devoted follower of Francesca's designs.  But below the satin and lace lies a heart of steel that drives her to take whatever she wants.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Cameron Tripod - Francesca's favorite but difficult photographer.  As Francesca's ex-lover, has he been over-exposed to her manipulation of his affections?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ron Dewing - He is the financial clout behind Francesca's salon.  But where does his money come from and what secrets thread through his life?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
